      <title>井喷的就业数据增加了美联储推迟或减少降息的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/blowout-jobs-report-raises-chance-of-delayed-fewer-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国近一年来最大的就业增长增加了美联储官员进一步推迟降息的可能性，并考虑今年的降息幅度少于预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/blowout-jobs-report-raises-chance-of-delayed-fewer-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 13:34:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
